column14: McKynzie is a very driven student athlete who enjoys building positive relationships to help grow her perspective.  Having worked at Chick-fil-A, she understands serving others and servant leadership.  McKynzie continues to grow her leadership talents on the Varsity softball team, the student athlete leadership group Sparta at Lincoln East,  and through serving others at Chick-fil-A.
